 Guides </LI>\r\n<P>Proposed release-date is 20 january 2004. </P>]]></FullText></attributes></article>','2008-01-21 12:44:41','New version',0,1,197,1,'mattias'),(173,3,'<?xml version=\'1.0\' encoding=\'UTF-8\'?><article xmlns=\'x-schema:ArticleSchema.xml\'><attributes><Name><![CDATA[Basic IG Page]]></Name><Template><![CDATA[<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\r\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\r\n<head>\r\n<title>$templateLogic.pageTitle</title>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"content-type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\r\n\r\n<meta name=\"author\" content=\"The InfoGlue Community\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"InfoGlue the Open Source Content Management System, based on Java , XML and Open Source.\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"InfoGlue, Java, J2EE, Jarkarta, Apache, Tomcat, OSS, Open Source, Linux, Solution, Content, Management, Software, Development, Free, GPL, Portal, Portlets\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"publisher\" content=\"The InfoGlue Community\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"publisher-email\" content=\"info@infoglue.org\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"copyright\" content=\"Copyright The InfoGlue community 2003. All rights reserved.\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"identifier-url\" content=\"http://www.infoglue.org\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"page-topic\" content=\"java open source software\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"language\" content=\"en\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"rating\" content=\"general\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"distribution\" content=\"global\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"dc.title\" content=\"InfoGlue the Open Source Content Management System, based on Java , XML and Open Source.\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"dc.creator\" content=\"The InfoGlue Community\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"classification\" content=\"InfoGlue, Java, J2EE, Jarkarta, Apache, Tomcat, OSS, Open Source, Linux, Solution, Content, Management, Software, Development, Free, GPL\"/>\r\n<meta name=\"abstract\" cont