des the following:</p><ul><li>Top navigation</li><li>Footer navigation</li><li>CSS-inclusion</li><li>Search form</li><li>Language switch although not enabled here</li><li>Sitemap link</li><li>A google analytics tag</li><li>Most parts of the template parts can be customized without changing much in the html</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You can configure the component a lot. Look at the properties section below.</p>]]></Manual><GroupName><![CDATA[Basic Pages]]></GroupName></attributes></article>','2008-01-20 18:05:48','Completely new site templates',0,1,298,1,'mattias'),(259,3,'<?xml version=\'1.0\' encoding=\'UTF-8\'?><article xmlns=\'x-schema:ArticleSchema.xml\'><attributes><Name><![CDATA[Content components]]></Name></attributes></article>','2008-01-20 18:05:50','Completely new site templates',0,1,299,1,'mattias'),(260,3,'<?xml version=\'1.0\' encoding=\'UTF-8\'?><article xmlns=\'x-schema:ArticleSchema.xml\'><attributes><Template><![CDATA[<%@ taglib uri=\"infoglue-page\" prefix=\"page\" %>\r\n<%@ taglib uri=\"infoglue-common\" prefix=\"common\" %>\r\n<%@ taglib uri=\"infoglue-structure\" prefix=\"structure\" %>\r\n<%@ taglib uri=\"infoglue-content\" prefix=\"content\" %>\r\n<%@ taglib uri=\"infoglue-management\" prefix=\"management\" %>\r\n<%@ taglib uri=\"infoglue-page\" prefix=\"tl\" %>\r\n<%@ taglib uri=\"http://java.sun.com/jstl/core\" prefix=\"c\" %>\r\n<%@ taglib uri=\"http://java.sun.com/jstl/fmt\" prefix=\"fmt\"%>\r\n\r\n<page:pageContext id=\"pc\"/>\r\n<page:deliveryContext id=\"dc\"/>\r\n\r\n<content:boundContents id=\"articles\" propertyName=\"Articles\"/>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"font-size: 50pt; padding-top: 300px;\">Print headline</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"font-size: 20pt;\">Print example</h3>\r\n<h1 style=\"font-size: 20pt; padding-bottom: 100px;\">Author: Mattias Bogeblad</h1>\r\n<p style=\"page-break-after: always\"></p>\r\n\r\n<c:set var=\"index\" value=\"1\"/>\r\n<c:forEach var=\"articleContent\" items=\"${articles}\">\r\n\r\n	<content:contentAttribute id=\"title